  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This approach has been commonly used in several state-of-the-art methods in different domains including Biological relation extraction,e.g.",
    "Bi-LSTM [50], MCCNN [51], GK [52], NHGK [53], EDG ([54], PIPE [42], WWSK [55], RCNN [56], DNN [57], RNN + CNN [56] and iLSTM+tAttn [41].",
    "We used a token length of 256 for BioInfer, HPRD50, IEPA, and LLL.",
    "The smaller datasets, HPRD50, IEPA, and LLL, required 20 epochs for fine-tuning, whereas the larger dataset,, BioInfer, achieved stability in just 10 epochs.",
    "The performance of the proposed RE with the improved entity-labelling schema (Stage 2 of GIX), compared with other state-of-the-art methods, is given in Table 3."
  ],
